summary:
A Business Innovation student who is focused and ready to explore the world of social innovation through product (re)design. I look forward to helping companies add societal values yet achieve their objectives.
I am also interested in emerging technology like Block-chain and how it can be used to grow businesses and improve society.
My skills include but  not limited to  design thinking and problem-solving, customer service and relationship management, imparting knowledge, communication and computer skills and still growingðŸ˜Š as I engage in personal studying and learning every day. I am known for my strong personality, have a can-do-it spirit and am also a great team player.
